                          Version 1.2 (12-02-99)

  This is the UNREGISTERED version of NetDock. You can distribute this
  version to whoever you want, but under no circumstances can you 
  distribute the REGISTERED version of the program (or PathPrefs)

  This program is supplied 'AS IS' and any damage which may be done to you
  or your computer is not the responsibility of Joker Developments or
  Gareth Griffiths. You decide whether to use this program, and if you do
  use it, any damage is your responsibility.

  This program has been tested extensively on a number of machines, these
  include:-

     An A1200 w/ 68020, 10MB RAM, 773MB HD, 8x CD-ROM and 56k Modem.                                                  
     An A1200 w/ 68020, 2MB RAM, 773MB HD.

