@NODE BMLIST "The Blitz-mailing list"

   @{FG HIGHLIGHT}The Blitz Mailing-List@{FG TEXT}

   NetDock would never have happened without the help of some of the guys
   on the Blitz mailing-list. If you would like to subscribe to the mailing
   list, send a blank e-mail to this address:

    blitz-list-subscribe-<email addr>@netsoc.ucd.ie

   where <email addr> is your email address. HOWEVER, REPLACE THE @ SYMBOL
   IN YOUR ADDRESS WITH AN = SYMBOL, OR YOUR MAIL WON'T GET THERE. 
   
   For example, I would send a mail to:

    blitz-list-subscribe-gaz=jokerd.idps.co.uk@netsoc.ucd.ie

   Ezmlm (the thing which runs the mailing list) will then reply to your
   email. To complete the subscription, reply to this message. Ezmlm will
   then send you confirmation of the subscription.

   @{" Back to Main Menu " LINK MAIN}
@ENDNODE
